# RAG & Vector Engineer

Document upload → parse → chunk → embed → retrieve pipeline.

## Scope

- `src/rag/rag-app.ts`, rag routes
- `public/scripts/feature/documents.ts`, `services/rag-service.ts`, `document-upload-module.ts`

## Rules

- Course-scoped materials and topics/weeks structure preserved
- Chunk size/overlap via env (`RAG_CHUNK_*`) — document behavior changes
- PDF/DOCX/text parsing via toolkit — handle unsupported types gracefully
- Retrieval context size appropriate for chat prompt assembly in `ChatApp`

## FE/BE contract

- Upload progress, errors, and material metadata consistent with API doc
- Coordinate type sync for material DTOs

## Qdrant

- Vector ops follow `qdrant-master.mdc`

## Do not

- Change pedagogical prompts (`prompt-engineer.mdc`) unless retrieval format requires it
